dtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F201-adam-gilchrist-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAdam%20Gilchrist%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Michael%20Vaughan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F427-michael-vaughan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMichael%20Vaughan%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20podcast%2C%20Maxwell%20said%20that%20the%20players%20of%20a%20subcontinent%20team%20like%20Afghanistan%20would%20start%20fighting%20amongst%20themselves%2C%20if%20he%20managed%20to%20stay%20on%20crease%20for%20a%20longer%20duration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20energy%20that%20they%20had%20in%20the%20first%2015-20%20overs%20was%20extraordinary%20and%20we%20have%20seen%20that%20a%20lot%20from%20them.%20I%20have%20played(against)%20a%20lot%20of%20subcontinental%20teams%20and%20one%20thing%20I%20have%20always%20found%20that%20if%20you%20could%20take%20the%20sting%20out%20of%20the%20game%2C%20not%20by%20runs%20but%20by%20basically%20being%20there%2C%20you%20play%20one%20or%20two%20shots%20in%20every%20couple%20of%20overs%20and%20you%20can%20see%20how%20flat%20it%20starts%20to%20get.%20They%20start%20a%20bit%20of%20bickering%2C%20infighting%2C%20finger-pointing%2C%20arms-raising%2C%20fielders%20not%20paying%20attention%2C%20it%20sort%20of%20starts%20to%20unravel%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maxwell%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DycjsqzuraS8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClub%20Prairie%20Fire%20Podcast.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaxwell%20further%20said%20that%20his%C2%A0experience%20in%20playing%20golf%20helped%20him%20play%20some%20unique%20shots%20during%20his%20double%20ton%20against%20Afghanistan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20got%20a%20lot%20to%20do%20with%20positions%20I%20get%20myself%20into%20on%20the%20golf%20course%20where%20I'm%20stuck%20behind%20a%20tree%20and%20I%20have%20to%20turn%20my%20wrist%20around.%20Flick%20it%20around.%20It%20allows%20you%20to%20be%20inventive.%20One%20of%20things%20I%20use