tps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67378875.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Japan'%20gets%20a%20good%20opening%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699679263000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105140169%2Cimgsize-739738.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fbox-office%2Fjapan-box-office-collection-kathi-starrer-gets-a-good-opening-in-tamil-nadu%2Farticleshow%2F105139778.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105139778.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BJapan%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20heist%20action%20drama%20directed%20by%20Raju%20Murugan%2C%20stars%20Karthi%2C%20Anu%20Emmanuel%2C%20Sunil%2C%20KS%20Ravikumar%2C%20and%20Vijay%20Milton.%20The%20film%20received%20a%20positive%20response%20from%20fans%2C%20with%20Karthi's%20performance%20being%20praised.%20Despite%20clashing%20with%20%26quot%3BJigarthana%20Double%20X%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20%26quot%3BJapan%26quot%3B%20emerged%20as%20the%20more%20successful%20film%2C%20grossing%20Rs%202.5%20crore.%20However%2C%20the%20Diwali%20releases%20affected%20the%20movie's%20box%20office%20collection%2C%20and%20it%20did%20not%20meet%20the%20initial%20predictions.%20Overall%2C%20%26quot%3BJapan%26quot%3B%20had%20a%20good%20opening%20and%20was%20well-received%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20the%20Telugu%20states.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHad%20The%20Umpires...%26quot%3B%3A%20MCC%20On%20Mathews'%20'Video%20Proof'%20After%20Being%20Timed%20Out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20controversy%20erupted%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20earlier%20this%20week%20as%20Sri%20Lanka%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Angelo%20Mathews%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1260-angelo-mathews-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAngelo%20Mathews%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20the%20first%20batter%20in%20the%20146-year%20history%20of%20international%20cricket%20to%20be%20timed%20out.%20Mathews%20arrived%20at%20the%20crease%20after%20the%20two-minute%20deadline%2C%20following%20Sadeera%20Samarawickrama's%20dismissal%2C%20due%20to%20an%20equipment%20malfunction.%20The%20former%20Sri%20Lanka%20captain%20was%20left%20fuming%20as%20he%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20fourth%20umpire%2C%20and%20also%20labelled%20Bangladesh%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shakib%20Al%20Hasan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F792-shakib-al-hasan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShakib%20Al%20Hasan%3C%2Fa%3E's%20act%20as%20%26quot%3Bdisgraceful%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMathews%20later%20shared%20a%20%26quot%3Bvideo%20evidence%26quot%3B%20showing%20that%20he%20still%20had%20%26quot%3B5%20more%20seconds%26quot%3B%2C%20posting%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20exact%20time%20of%20Samarawickrama's%20dismissal%20and%20that%20of%20his%20arrival%20at%20the%20crease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mathews%20alleged%20that%20the%20umpires%20made%20a%20mistake%2C%20the%20Marylebone%20Cricket%20Club%20(MCC)%2C%20the%20custodians%20of%20the%20game%2C%20has%20shared%20a%20statement%20regarding%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20the%20MCC%20argued%20Mathews%20should%20have%20signalled%20to%20the%20umpires%20when%20his%20helmet%20strap%20broke%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20officials%20would%20have%20given%20him%20extra%20time%20to%20sort%20out%20his%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHad%20the%20umpires%20been%20informed%20of%20a%20significant%2C%20justifiable%2C%20equipment-related%20delay%20within%20the%20two-minute%20allowance%2C%20they%20could%20have%20treated%20it%20as%20a%20new%20type%20of%20delay%20(as%20they%20would%20when%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20bat%20breaks)%2C%20possibly%20even%20calling%20Time%2C%20allowing%20for%20a%20resolution%20of%20that%20delay%20without%20the%20batter%20being%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20Timed%20out.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20both%20umpires%20determined%20the%20delay%20came%20after%20the%20two%20minutes%20had%20elapsed%2C%20and%20that%20Time%20had%20not%20been%20called%20before%20the%20appeal%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxsports.com.au%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fno-other-action-to-take-mcc-heaps-blame-on-sri-lanka-star-for-controversial-timed-out-wicket%2Fnews-story%2F293963f677d0148ec24d192746bd6c9b%5C%22%3EFox%20Sports%20Australia%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20MCC%20as%20saying%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20taken%20more%20than%2090%20seconds%20to%20get%20to%20the%2030-yard%20circle%2C%20Mathews%20appeared%20to%20notice%20that%20he%20was%20short%20on%20time%2C%20jogging%20the%20final%20few%20yards%20to%20the%20wicket.%20His%20helmet%20malfunction%20has%20since%20been%20shown%20to%20have%20taken%20place%201%20minute%20and%2054%20seconds%20after%20the%20previous%20wicket%20had%20fallen.%20He%20had%20not%2C%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20begun%20to%20take%20guard%20and%20was%20not%20close%20to%20being%20in%20a%20position%20to%20receive%20the%20ball.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20helmet%20broke%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20Mathews%20did%20not%20consult%20with%20the%20umpires%2C%20which%20a%20player%20would%20be%20expected%20to%20do%20when%20seeking%20new%20equipment.%20Rather%2C%20he%20just%20signalled%20to%20the%20dressing%20room%20for%20a%20replacement.%20Had%20he%20explained%20to%20the%20umpires%20what%20had%20happened%20and%20asked%20for%20time%20to%20get%20it%20sorted%20out%2C%20they%20might%20have%20allowed%20him%20to%20change%20the%20helmet%2C%20perhaps%20calling%20Time%20and%20thus%20removing%20any%20possibility%20of%20being%20Timed%20out.%20Given%20that%20Time%20had%20not%20been%20called%2C%20and%20that%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20appeal%20more%20than%20two%20minutes%20had%20elapsed%2C%20the%20umpires%20correctly%20gave%20Mathews%20out.%20In%20fact%2C%20there%20was%20no%20other%20action%20for%20the%20umpires%20to%20take%20within%20the%20Laws%20of%20Cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699679100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fn8cn8c88_angelo-mathews-afp_625x300_11_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fhad-the-umpires-mcc-issues-clarification-on-angelo-mathews-video-proof-against-being-timed-out-4566108%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Angelo%20Mathews%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20umpires%20had%20made%20a%20mistake%2C%20sharing%20a%20%26quot%3Bvideo%20evidence%26quot%3B%20showing%20that%20he%20still%20had%20%26quot%3B5%20more%20seconds%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A76%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fhad-the-umpires-mcc-issues-clarification-on-angelo-mathews-video-proof-against-being-timed-out-4566108%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fhad-the-umpires-mcc-issues-clarification-on-angelo-mathews-video-proof-against-being-timed-out-4566108%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fhad-the-umpires-mcc-issues-clarification-on-angelo-mathews-video-proof-against-being-timed-out-4566108%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PC%20did%20not%20'feel%20pretty'%20post%20Miss%20World%20win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699679012000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105140040%2Cimgsize-253993.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhy-did-priyanka-chopra-not-feel-