%2040%20feet%2C%20which%20is%20plenty%20for%20a%20home%20entertainment%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBluetooth%20devices%20can%20connect%20directly%20to%20the%20Nova%207X%20using%20the%20Bluetooth%20pairing%20button%20on%20the%20headset%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20sound%20delay%20compared%20to%20using%202.4GHz.%C2%A0%20However%2C%20the%20Nova%207X's%20Bluetooth%20range%20extends%20far%20beyond%20the%2040-foot%20range%20of%20the%202.4GHz%20transmitter.%20Though%20we%20weren't%20able%20to%20measure%20exactly%20how%20far%2C%20the%20Bluetooth%20range%20is%20at%20least%20several%20hundred%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nova%207X%20lasts%2035%20to%2040%20hours%20on%20a%20single%20charge%2C%20and%2015%20minutes%20of%20charging%20can%20yield%20six%20hours%20of%20play%20time.%20The%20battery%20life%20is%20comparable%20to%20other%20headsets%20in%20the%20same%20price%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20USB-C%20dongle%20functions%20just%20fine%2C%20it%20blocks%20the%20front-facing%20USB-A%20port%20of%20the%20PlayStation%205%20while%20plugged%20in%2C%20which%20feels%20like%20a%20bit%20of%20an%20oversight.%20While%20the%20PS5%20does%20have%20backwards%20facing%20USB-A%20ports%2C%20they%20can%20be%20a%20hassle%20to%20reach%20depending%20on%20your%20setup.%20Xbox%20consoles%20don't%20have%20a%20USB-C%20port%20at%20all%20so%20you'll%20need%20to%20use%20the%20included%20USB-C%20to%20USB-A%20adapter%20to%20connect%20the%20dongle.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20the%20Nintendo%20Switch%20dock.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20USB-C%20dongle%20can%20be%20plugged%20directly%20into%20the%20Switch%20in%20portable%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20if%20you%20do%20happen%20to%20want%20a%20wired%20connection%2C%20the%20Nova%207X%20has%20a%203.5mm%20port%20that%20can%20be%20connected%20to%20any%20device%20with%20a%20standard%20headphone%20jack%2C%20like%20the%20PlayStation%20and%20Xbox%20wireless%20controllers%2C%20and%20the%20Nintendo%20Switch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Performance%5C%22%3EThe%20Arctis%20Nova%207X%20delivers%20impressive%20sound%20quality%20and%20works%20well%20with%20spatial%20audio%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221022%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20showing%20performance%20of%20the%20SteelSeries%20GG%20EQ.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654e631336d588dc55ce8b59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22766%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESteelSeries%20has%20PC%20software%20called%20Sonar%20that%20lets%20you%20manage%20your%20EQ%20and%20spatial%20audio%20settings.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Webb%20%2F%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20playback%20quality%2C%20the%20Arctis%20Nova%207X%20ranks%20alongside%20the%20best%20headsets%20we've%20tested.%20It's%20fully%20capable%20of%20using%20spatial%20audio%20formats%20like%20PlayStation's%20Tempest%203D%20audio%2C%20Microsoft's%20Windows%20Sonic%2C%20and%20SteelSeries's%20own%20Sonar%20spatial%20audio.%20Dolby%20Atmos%20spatial%20audio%20is%20also%20compatible%2C%20but%20requires%20a%20paid%20license%20to%20use%20on%20Windows%20and%20Xbox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20gaming%20headsets%2C%20the%20Nova%207X%20has%20a%20bass-heavy%20sound%20profile%2C%20but%20deep%20tones%20rarely%20sound%20overwhelming%20or%20muddy.%20The%20headset%20also%20does%20a%20good%20job%20of%20isolating%20the%20direction%20of%20different%20in-game%20sounds%2C%20with%20or%20without%20spatial%20audio%20enabled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteelSeries%20offers%20a%20PC%20audio%20suite%20called%20Sonar%20that%20provides%20EQ%20and%20other%20adjustable%20sound%20settings.%20However%2C%20those%20settings%20don't%20carry%20over%20when%20you%20use%20the%20headset%20with%20consoles.%20You'll%20have%20to%20access%20the%20built-in%20EQs%20on%20Xbox%20or%20PlayStation%20to%20balance%20the%20audio%20on%20those%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArctis%20Nova%207X's%20microphone%20includes%20noise-cancellation%20to%20help%20eliminate%20background%20noise%20while%20you're%20speaking%2C%20and%20it%20also%20features%20a%20built-in%20monitor%20so%20you%20can%20hear%20how%20you%20sound%20in%20voice%20chat.%20However%2C%20the%20headset%20doesn't%20have%20active%20noise%20cancellation%20(ANC)%20for%20audio%20playback%3B%20that%20feature%20is%20reserved%20for%20the%20more%20expensive%20Arctis%20Nova%20Pro%20Wireless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20it%3F%5C%22%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20Arctis%20Nova%207X%20Headset%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22870%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20SteelSeries%20Arctis%20Nova%207X%20headsets%20leaning%20on%20an%20Xbox%20Series%20X%20next%20to%20a%20smartphone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64be8483ed4f46001961d4e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22653%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20SteelSeries%20Arctis%20Nova%207X%20is%20missing%20some%20high-end%20features%2C%20but%20it%20offers%20all%20the%20essentials%20for%20a%20reasonable%20price.%3Cp%3EBest%20Buy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20consider%20the%20Arctis%20Nova%207X%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-wireless-gaming-headsets%5C%22%3Ebest%20wireless%20gaming%20headset%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20console%20gamers%2C%20so%20if%20you%20play%20on%20Xbox%2C%20PlayStation%2C%20or%20Switch%2C%20it's%20a%20great%20choice%20that%20features%20nearly%20everything%20you%20could%20want%20for%20a%20midrange%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20bells%20and%20whistles%20missing%20that%20you%20could%20get%20on%20more%20expensive%20headsets.%20If%20you're%20a%20content%20creator%20or%20have%20a%20complex%20home%20setup%20with%20multiple%20speakers%2C%20the%20%24350%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsteelseries-arctis-nova-pro-wireless-gaming-headset-review%5C%22%3EArctis%20Nova%20Pro%20Wireless%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%2