%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20now%20moving%20towards%20EVs%2C%20there%20will%20soon%20be%20a%20huge%20gap%20in%20demand%20and%20supply%20of%20renewable%20electricity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20line%20of%20thought%20prompted%20me%20to%20consider%20a%20solution%20similar%20to%20the%20setup%20we%20employ%20in%20our%20homes%2C%20with%20electricity%20as%20the%20primary%20source%20and%20a%20generator%20or%20inverter%20as%20a%20backup.%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20we%20have%20an%20electric%20vehicle%20equipped%20with%20a%20petrol%20engine%20as%20a%20standby%20power%20source%20to%20ensure%20complete%20reliability%20for%20the%20consumer%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20the%20idea%20of%20Green%20Tiger%20Mobility%20came%20to%20Ashish.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20we%20built%20the%20hybrid%20as%20a%20retrofit%20solution%20to%20give%20a%20bridge%20to%2025%20crore%20existing%20two-wheeler%20riders%20in%20the%20country%20towards%20a%20greener%20tomorrow%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20in%20early%202020%2C%20Ashish%20decided%20to%20quit%20his%2015%20years%20of%20corporate%20career%20and%20finally%20bring%20his%20childhood%20dream%20to%20a%20living%20reality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20the%20company%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332299%2Fbengaluru-chef-elizabeth-yorke-upcycles-brewery-byproducts-into-sustainable-food-items%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresent%20in%20Bengaluru%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20has%20converted%20over%2050%20vehicles%20into%20their%20hybrid%20models.%20Of%20those%2025%20were%20brought%20to%20the%20company%20by%20the%20consumers%20themselves.%20It%20has%20received%20ARAI%20%26amp%3B%20RTO%20approval%20to%20convert%20all%20major%20brands%20of%20scooters%20up%20to%20125cc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20converted%20vehicles%20have%20undergone%20rigoro