20Clean%20Air'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F05162325%2FMahatma_Gandhi_at_Bhangi_sweepers_colony_New_Delhi.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20air%20pollution%20on%20the%20health%20and%20well-being%20of%20people%20in%20Delhi%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20India%20is%20a%20byproduct%20of%20modern%20civilisation%20founded%20on%20massive%20consumption%20of%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20and%20in%20the%20words%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cincessant%20multiplication%20of%20wants%20and%20desires%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20enormity%20of%20the%20crisis%20was%20reflected%20in%20the%20convening%20of%20the%20first-ever%20Global%20Conference%20on%20Air%20Pollution%20and%20Health%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20between%20October%2029%20and%20November%201%2C%202018.%20The%20WHO%20at%20that%20time%20had%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20world%20gets%20hotter%20and%20more%20crowded%2C%20our%20engines%20continue%20to%20pump%20out%20dirty%20emissions%2C%20and%20half%20the%20world%20has%20no%20access%20to%20clean%20fuels%20or%20technologies%20(e.g.%20stoves%2C%20lamps)%2C%20the%20very%20air%20we%20breathe%20is%20growing%20dangerously%20polluted%3A%20nine%20out%20of%20ten%20people%20now%20breathe%20polluted%20air%2C%20which%20kills%207%20million%20people%20every%20year%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20went%20on%20further%20to%20add%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20health%20effects%20of%20air%20pollution%20are%20serious%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20level%20that%20%E2%80%9Cone-third%20of%20deaths%20from%20stroke%2C%20lung%20cancer%2C%20and%20heart%20disease%20are%20due%20to%20air%20pollution%E2%80%9D.%20It%20sharply%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CAir%20pollution%20is%20hard%20to%20escape%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20rich%20an%20area%20you%20live%20in.%20It%20is%20all%20around%20us.%20Microscopic%20pollutants%20in%20the%20air%20can%20slip%20past%20our%20body%E2%80%99s%20defences%2C%20penetrating%20deep%20into%20our%20respiratory%20and%20circulatory%20system%2C%20damaging%20our%20lungs%2C%20heart%2C%20and%20brain.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20a%20hundred%20years%20back%20while%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20Gandhi%20wrote%20about%20air%20pollution%20caused%20by%20modern%20civilisation.%20On%20March%205%2C%201906%2C%20he%20wrote%20in%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Opinion%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CA%20man%20can%20do%20without%20food%20for%20several%20days%20and%20live%20a%20day%20altogether%20without%20water%2C%20but%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20carry%20on%20without%20air%20even%20for%20a%20minute.%20If%20a%20thing%20that%20is%20so%20very%20vital%20to%20life%20is%20not%20pure%2C%20the%20result%20cannot%20but%20be%20deleterious.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20the%20constricted%20areas%20and%20narrow%20spaces%20of%20London%20marked%20by%20deficiencies%20of%20clean%20air%20Gandhi%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20matter%20deserves%20consideration%20by%20Indian%20leaders.%20We%20suffer%20much%20because%20we%20do%20not%20realise%20the%20value%20of%20pure%20air%2C%20and%20this%20again%20is%20a%20strong%20reason%20why%20diseases%20like%20plague%20spread%20among%20us.%E2%80%9D%20Those%20words%20sound%20so%20contemporary%20when%20our%20leaders%20hardly%20do%20anything%20to%20deal%20with%20increasing%20air%20pollution%20faced%20by%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fdelhi-air-quality-in-severe-category-no-respite-from-pollution-in-sight%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Air%20Quality%20in%20%E2%80%98Severe%E2%80%99%20Category%2C%20No%20Respite%20from%20Pollution%20in%20Sight%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0He%20also%20wrote%20a%20series%20of%20pieces%20under%20the%20caption%20%E2%80%9CGeneral%20Knowledge%20on%20Health%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Opinion%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20one%20such%20piece%20published%20on%20February%201%2C%201913%2C%20under%20the%20heading%20%E2%80%98Air%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20observed%20that%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20human%20body%20depended%20on%20air%2C%20water%2C%20and%20food%20and%20described%20air%20as%20the%20most%20essential.%20He%20then%20presciently%20wrote%20with%20anguish%20%E2%80%9Cmodern%20civilisation%20has%20put%20a%20price%20even%20on%20air%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20provided%20by%20nature%20at%20no%20cost.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20these%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20sharply%20remarked%2C%20%E2%80%9Cone%20has%20to%20go%20off%20to%20distant%20places%20to%20take%20the%20air%2C%20and%20this%20costs%20money.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20words%20of%20Gandhi%20resonate%20in%20the%20present%20context%20when%20people%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20several%20other%20parts%20of%20India%20are%20breathing%20air%2C%20which%20as%20per%20the%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20is%20hazardous%20and%20dangerous%20for%20health%20and%20well-being.%20Scores%20of%20people%20are%20leaving%20Delhi%20to%20the%20hills%20or%20far-off%20places%20in%20search%20of%20clean%20air%20for%20breathing%20and%20in%20the%20words%20of%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20costs%20money%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13184606%2FPollution.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13184606%2FPollution.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13184606%2FPollution-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13184606%2FPollution-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672880%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPeople%20exercise%20near%20the%20India%20Gate%20amid%20heavy%20smog%20in%20New%20Delhi%20Photo%3A%20Kabir%20Jhangiani%2FAlamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20leaving%20the%20cities%20and%20proceeding%20to%20far-off%20places%20to%20avoid%20highly%20polluted%20air%2C%20people%20are%20buying%20air%20purifiers%20for%20their%20workplaces%20and%20homes.%20All%20such%20developments%20hardly%20known%20two%20or%20three%20decades%20back%20affirm%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20prophetic%20warning%20that%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6modern%20civilisation%20has%20put%20a%20price%20even%20on%20air.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20illuminating%20to%20note%20that%20he%20while%20indicting%20modern%20civilisation%20for%20polluting%20air%20and%20putting%20a%20price%20tag%20on%20clean%20air%20interpreted%20Swaraj%20in%20terms%20of%20access%20of%20people%20to%20clean%20air%2C%20water%2C%20and%20grain.%20It%20is%20well%20known%20that%20Swaraj%20or%20independence%20of%20India%20was%20looked%20at%20by%20him%20from%20the%20perspectives%20of%20Hindu-Muslim%20Unity%2C%20abolition%20of%20untouchability%2C%20economic%20equality%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%2C%20etc.%20While%20addressing%20a%20meeting%20on%20January%201%2C%201918%2C%20in%20Ahmedabad%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20insufficient%20and%20irregular%20supply%20of%20water%20by%20the%20Ahmedabad%20Municipality%2C%20Gandhi%20talked%20about%20air%2C%20water%2C%20and%20grain%20and%20described%20them%20as%20aspects%20of%20Swaraj%20and%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9CAir%20is%20free%20to%20all%2C%20but%2C%20if%20it%20is%20polluted%2C%20it%20harms%20our%20health.%20Doctors%20say%20that%20bad%20air%20is%20more%20harmful%20than%20bad%20water.%20Inhalation%20of%20bad%20air%20is%20harmful%20by%20itself%20and%20this%20is%20the%20reason%20we%20sometimes%20need%20a%20change%20of%20air.%E2%80%9D%20Employing%20the%20meaning%20of%20Swaraj%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20clean%20air%20and%20water%2C%20it%20can%20be%20asserted%20that%20there%20is%20no%20Swaraj%20in%20large%20parts%20of%20India%20because%20of%20the%20severity%20of%20air%20pollution%20and%20deficiency%20of%20portable%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%201931%2C%20he%20reflected%20on%20just%20administration%20and%20wrote%20that%20in%20%3Cem%3ERam%20Rajya%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20in%20People%E2%80%99s%20Raj%2C%20which%20he%20described%20as%20a%20democracy%20where%20both%20the%20rulers%20and%20the%20ruled%20would%20get%20equal%20access%20to%20clean%20air%20and%20clean%20water.%20Mounting%20air%20pollution%20in%20India%20and%20crises%20caused%20by%20the%20drinking%20water%20shortage%20in%20our%20country%20represent%20the%20devaluation%20of%20our%20democracy%20and%20governance.%20It%20is%20in%20this%20context%20important%20to%20revisit%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20ideas%20on%20air%20pollution%2C%20clean%20air%2C%20and%20clean%20water%20to%20fine-tune%20our%20governance%20and%20transition%20from%20a%20fossil%20fuel-based%20carbon%20economy%20to%20a%20clean%20and%20sustainable%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20Served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K%20R%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699594215000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F05162325%2FMahatma_Gandhi_at_Bhangi_sweepers_colony_New_Delhi.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fgandhi-presciently-said-in-1913-that-modern-civilisation-has-put-a-price-tag-on-clean-air%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Those%20words%20of%20Gandhi%20resonate%20in%20the%20present%20context%20when%20people%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20several%20other%20parts%20of%20India%20are%20breathing%20air%20which%20is%20dangerous%20for%20health%20and%20well-being.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fgandhi-presciently-said-in-1913-that-modern-civilisation-has-put-a-price-tag-on-clean-air%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%2