sations%20have%20now%20written%20an%20open%20letter%20which%20describes%20the%20injuries%20sustained%20by%20the%20engineer.%20The%20attack%20resulted%20in%2022%20broken%20bones%2C%20he%20was%20left%20nearly%20dead%2C%20and%20he%20is%20still%20in%20hospital%2C%20more%20than%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20years%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20incident%20the%20BJP%20attacked%20the%20Congress%2C%20accusing%20Malinga%20of%20hooliganism%20and%20creating%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgoonda%20raj%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20state.%20Dalit%20groups%20had%20criticised%20the%20Congress%20and%20had%20collectively%20appealed%20to%20the%20party%20to%20deny%20him%20a%20ticket%20in%20these%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20open%20letter%20first%20asks%2C%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A1%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A1%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%80%2C%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%80%2C%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%20%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BF%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%AE%20%3F%20(Nadda%20ji%2C%20Modi%20ji%2C%20Is%20this%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20Dalit-Valmikis%3F)%20It%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20express%20shock%20at%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20has%20welcomed%20Malinga%20into%20the%20party.%20The%20letter%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20responsible%20leaders%20of%20your%20party%20in%20Rajasthan%20spoke%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20criticised%20Girraj%20Singh%20Malinga%20gave%20us%20hope%20that%20the%20accused%20will%20be%20punished%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20then%20adds%20that%20instead%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20are%20shocked%20that%20a%20man%20accused%20of%20Dalit%20atrocities%20was%2C%20with%20much%20fanfare%20and%20joy%2C%20taken%20into%20the%20BJP%20and%20on%20that%20occasion%2C%20Union%20minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20distributed%20sweets%20and%20w