20of%20India%20(NHAI)%20for%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20raises%20questions%20over%20how%20chief%20secretary%20Naresh%20Kumar%20may%20have%20handled%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20plot%20in%20question%20was%20to%20be%20acquired%20from%20two%20Delhi%20businessmen%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20is%20related%20by%20marriage%20to%20the%20promoter%20of%20a%20realty%20firm%20where%20Naresh%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20son%20works.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20concerns%20have%20been%20raised%20about%20a%20potential%20conflict%20of%20interest%2C%20the%20chief%20secretary%20denies%20any%20wrongdoing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20case%20in%20question%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20May%20this%20year%2C%20the%20district%20magistrate%20(DM)%20of%20south%20west%20Delhi%20awarded%20Rs%20353%20crore%20as%20compensation%20to%20two%20individuals%20for%2019%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Bamnoli%20village%20for%20a%20road%20project%20%E2%80%93%20at%20the%20rate%20of%20Rs%2018.54%20crore%20per%20acre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20land%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20be%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eacquired%20for%20NHAI%E2%80%99s%20Dwarka%20Expressway.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20doing%20so%2C%20DM%20Hemant%20Kumar%20overturned%20a%202018%20decision%20by%20the%20adjudicating%20authority%2C%20the%20additional%20district%20magistrate%2C%20granting%20compensation%20of%20Rs%2041.52%20crore%20for%20the%20same%20parcel%20of%20land%20based%20on%20a%20valuation%20of%20Rs%2053%20lakh%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20grounds%20cited%20to%20justify%20a%20whopping%20nine-fold%20increase%20in%20compensation%20was%20that%20the%20land%20was%20now%20deemed%20to%20be%20a%20low-density%20residential%20area%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20not%20agricultural%20as%20was%20initially%20made%20out%20to%20be.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Therefore%2C%20it%20needed%20to%20be%20compensated%20at%20a%20higher%20rate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20hiked%20compensation%20were%20Subhash%20Chand%20Kathuria%20and%20his%20brother%2C%20Vinod%20Kathuria.%20Subhash%20Kathuria%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20father-in-law%20of%20Aman%20Sarin%2C%20who%20is%20the%20promoter%20of%20a%20realty%20firm%2C%20Anantraj%20Limited.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESarin%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20close%20business%20links%20with%20Karan%20Chauhan%2C%20son%20of%20Delhi%20chief%20secretary%20Naresh%20Kumar%2C%20and%20it%20is%20this%20association%20which%20has%20triggered%20questions%20over%20a%20potential%20conflict%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20compensation%20was%20hiked%20on%20May%2015%2C%202023%20and%20the%20NHAI%20took%20note%20almost%20immediately.%20The%20DM%E2%80%99s%20decision%20would%20lead%20to%20huge%20cost%20overruns%20on%20other%20road%20projects%2C%20the%20NHAI%20said%2C%20as%20it%20moved%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Delhi%20high%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20problem%20of%20cost%20overruns%20has%20been%20haunting%20NHAI.%20A%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-finds-irregularities-in-award-of-highway-projects-under-bharatmala-pariyojana%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erecent%20CAG%20audit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esaw%20the%20government%20auditor%20flagging%20the%20huge%20overrun%20from%20the%20approved%20amount%20of%20Rs%2018.2%20crore%20per%20kilometre%20rising%20multi-fold%20to%20nearly%20Rs%20251%20crore%20per%20km%2C%20or%2014-times%2C%20within%20a%20very%20short%20span%20of%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKaran%20Chauhan%20and%20Anant%20Raj%20Ltd%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKaran%20Chauhan%2C%20son%20of%20the%20Delhi%20chief%20secretary%2C%20is%20an%20employee%20of%20Anantraj%20Ltd%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20being%20a%20director%20in%20three%20other%20companies%2C%20some%20of%20which%20have%20links%20to%20Anantraj.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Anantraj%20Limited%20group%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CKaran%20is%20our%20employee%20since%2001st%20June%202019%20like%20any%20other%20employee%20of%20our%20Company%20and%20is%20working%20in%20the%20field%20of%20development%20of%20data%20centres%20which%20we%20are%20developing.%20We%20appoint%20some%20employees%20as%20Directors%2C%20as%20per%20policy%20and%20legal%20requirements.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20web%20of%20connections%20is%20unusual%20for%20a%20mere%20employer-employee%20relationship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20only%20do%20Chauhan%E2%80%99s%20companies%20and%20Anantraj%20Ltd%20and%20its%20various%20verticals%20have%20common%20directors%2C%20but%20the%20postal%20address%20in%20the%20case%20of%20some%20of%20these%20companies%20is%20the%20same%20as%20that%20of%20the%20realty%20firm%2C%20as%20is%20the%20email%20address.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Big%20Town%20Properties%20Pvt%20Ltd%20is%20a%20company%20with%20Chauhan%20as%20a%20director.%20As%20per%20ROC%20records%2C%20the%20registered%20email%20address%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20Manoj%20Pahwa%2C%20an%20employee%20who%20has%20been%20company%20secretary%20to%20the%20Anantraj%20group%20since%201993.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManoj%20Kumar%20is%20a%20director%20at%20Big%20Town%20Properties%2C%20as%20is%20Narayan%20Singh%20Rajpoot.%20As%20senior%20GM%20(operations)%2C%20Rajpoot%20is%20a%20key%20team%20member%20of%20Anantraj%20Limited%20in%20addition%20to%20being%20director%20at%20several%20other%20Anantraj%20group%20verticals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPuneet%20Kumar%20Bajpai%20is%20also%20a%20director%20at%20Big%20Town%20Properties%20as%20well%20as%20a%20director%20at%20other%20Anantraj%20group%20verticals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20postal%20address%20for%20Big%20Town%20Properties%20is%20the%20same%20as%20that%20of%20many%20Anantraj%20group%20firms%20located%20at%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20Manesar%20address.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20February%202022%2C%20Karan%20Chauhan%20has%20also%20been%20a%20director%20at%20ES%20Health%20Care%20Private%20Limited.%20The%20email%20address%20provided%20while%20setting%20up%20this%20company%20belongs%20to%20the%20Anantraj%20group%20domain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnish%20Sarin%2C%20other%20than%20being%20a%20promoter%20of%20Anantraj%20Limited%2C%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Metamix%20Tech.%20Karan%20Chauhan%20is%20also%20listed%20as%20the%20founder%20of%20this%20company.%20The%20email%20address%20is%20one%20which%20several%20Anantraj%20verticals%20share.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChief%20secretary%20says%20son%20%E2%80%98not%20dependent%20on%20me%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09183804%2Fnaresh-kumar_0.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22173%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684341%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22220%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENaresh%20Kumar.%20Photo%3A%20delhi.gov.in%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENaresh%20Kumar%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20son%20Sh.%20Karan%20Chauhan%20works%20with%20a%20listed%20public%20limited%20company%20Anant%20Raj%20Housing%20Ltd.%20since%20June%202019.%20He%20is%20also%20not%20dependent%20on%20me.%20Neither%20I%20know%20about%20the%20relationship%20between%20Directors%20of%20Anant%20Raj%20Housing%20Ltd.%20with%20Sh.%20Subhash%20Kathuria%2C%20nor%20there%20was%20any%20occasion%20by%20which%20I%20would%20have%20known%20about%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20Karan%20Chauhan.%20The%20copy%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20he%20responds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESuspending%20the%20DM%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chief%20secretary%20has%20been%20at%20pains%20to%20distance%20himself%20from%20the%20entire%20affair.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20questions%20about%20his%20role%20in%20not%20declaring%20the%20potential%20conflict%20of%20interest%20when%20NHAI%20raised%20an%20alarm%20in%20the%20summer%20remain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%2C%20sources%20say%20that%20once%20NHAI%20raised%20the%20alarm%2C%20the%20matter%20should%20have%20rested%20there%20because%20the%20DM%20was%20acting%20in%20his%20judicial%20capacity%20and%20his%20decision%20was%20anyway%20being%20challenged%20in%20court.%20Instead%2C%20the%20chief%20secretary%20recommended%20action%20against%20the%20DM%2C%20which%20set%20in%20motion%20a%20chain%20of%20events%20by%20other%20government%20departments%20which%20led%20to%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20transfer%20away%20from%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20DM%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20raise%20compensation%20was%20%E2%80%9Csuspect%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20his%20immediate%20superior%2C%20the%20divisional%20commissioner%2C%20made%20it%20out%20to%20be%2C%20then%20the%20matter%20should%20have%20gone%20to%20the%20National%20Capital%20Civil%20Services%20Authority%20(NCSSA)%20headed%20by%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20September%2019%2C%20the%20file%20was%20sent%20back%20to%20the%20chief%20secretary%20by%20LG%20Saxena.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20DM%20was%20suspended%20soon%20after%2C%20and%20a%20CBI%20probe%20ordered%20on%20October%2021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESurprisingly%2C%20Hemant%20Kumar%20was%20also%20transferred%20out%20to%20the%20Andaman%20Islands.%20Delhi%20government%20sources%20say%20they%20suspect%20the%20reason%20Hemant%20Kumar%20was%20transferred%20out%20was%20that%20the%20NCCSA%20could%20have%20summoned%20the%20files%20and%20Kejriwal%20could%20have%20had%20a%20say%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20shifting%20him%20to%20a%20full%20Union%20Territory%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20ensured%20that%20the%20heat%20is%20off%20the%20officer%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20Delhi%20government%20source%2C%20speaking%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20his%20part%2C%20Naresh%20Kumar%20says%20it%20was%20the%20MHA%20which%20decided%20to%20transfer%20Hemant%20Kumar%20and%20that%20he%20had%20%E2%80%9Cno%20role.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20not%20able%20to%20independently%20confirm%20the%20reasons%20for%20moving%20the%20suspended%20former%20DM%20from%20Delhi%20to%20the%20Andamans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20pursuant%20to%20the%20matter%20in%20court%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ENHAI%20vs%20Subhash%20Chand%20Kathuriya%3C%2Fem%3E%20case%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20on%20October%2031%20cancelled%20the%20DM%E2%80%99s%20order%20to%20raise%20compensation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EShadow%20on%20CBI%20Inquiry%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20is%20now%20looking%20into%20the%20matter%20but%20sources%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government%20are%20asking%20how%20impartial%20the%20probe%20will%20be%20given%20the%20potential%20conflict%20of%20interest.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20secretary%20insists%20there%20is%20no%20conflict.%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20seems%20that%20your%20query%20has%20been%20drafted%20in%20a%20manner%20to%20sling%20mud%20on%20me%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20actual%20delinquent%20officer%20who%20did%20this%20misconduct%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ENaresh%20Kumar%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Are%20you%20siding%20with%20the%20officer%20who%20passed%20such%20an%20order%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENaresh%20Kumar%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20seems%20that%20some%20disgruntled%20elements%20against%20whom%20action%20has%20been%20taken%2Fis%20being%20taken%2C%20including%20related%20with%20Delhi%20Excise%20Scam%20and%20Sheesh%20Mahal%20matter%2C%20are%20trying%20to%20circulate%20false%20and%20fabricated%20complaints.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20you%20haven%E2%80%99t%20shared%20any%20complaint(s)%2C%20I%20request%20you%20to%20share%20such%20complaint(s)%20so%20that%20replies%20to%20the%20same%20be%20provided%20to%20you%2C%20and%20actions%20as%20per%20law%20may%20be%20taken%20against%20such%20disgruntled%20elements%20who%20made%20such%20false%20and%20motivated%20complaint(s)%E2%80%A6In%20case%20of%20publication%20of%20factually%20incorrect%20information%2C%20I%20reserve%20my%20rights%20to%20take%20appropriate%20action.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHemant%20Kumar%2C%20the%20former%20DM%20who%20was%20transferred%2C%20has%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20queries.%20His%20response%20will%20be%20incorporated%20if%20and%20when%20he%20responds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699538463000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09183625%2F40216917384_1f67aedecb_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-chief-secretary-nhai-land-compensation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%