lding%20Sangopita.%20Akshay%20is%20also%20doing%20much%20better%20and%20has%20developed%20well%20in%20these%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20them%20wings%20to%20fly%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201498px)%20100vw%2C%201498px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221498%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20are%2062%20children%20in%20Sangopita%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529.jpeg%201498w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529-300x176.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529-500x293.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529-768x450.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529-150x88.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333895%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThere%20are%2062%20children%20in%20Sangopita%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20children%20seem%20to%20have%20found%20their%20happy%20place%2C%20their%20parents%20describe%20Sangopita%20as%20a%20nurturing%20and%20thriving%20playground%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERaj%20(16)%C2%A0%20has%20autism%20and%20is%20hyperactive%2C%20according%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20Swapna.%20A%20single%20mother%20who%20stays%20with%20her%20aged%20parents%2C%20she%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20look%20after%20him.%20Her%20parents%20weren%E2%80%99t%20equipped%20to%20deal%20with%20him%20when%20she%20went%20to%20work%20either.%20Raj%20was%20susceptible%20to%20getting%20fits%20as%20wel